      "id": "PopularPost72163",
      "post_content": "[Nourish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nourish) laughs at this garbage.   \n  \nOn the plus side, I like the flavor of the card. Is it just me, or is there a lot of the Urza/Gerrard/Mirri/Hanna etc. saga directly printed and quoted on magic cards? Maybe that was just a phase Magic went through, but I think mentioning story characters goes a long way towards adding truly memorable characters to the game.   \n  \nI've never even read the storyline here, but at least it makes me want to learn more. I suppose they stopped doing that so much because it would be confusing to new players.   \n  ",
